NOTE ON EXPORT-CONTROLLED CONTENT
=================================
Templates in this repository are designed to be invoked against ITAR /
export-controlled customer documentation in deployments where the framework
is configured for the appropriate data-sensitivity tier. The templates and
schemas themselves do not contain export-controlled technical data and are
released under the MIT license above. Operators are responsible for ensuring
that any documents passed to a template at runtime are handled in compliance
with applicable export-control law (ITAR / EAR), and for selecting a backend
that satisfies their compliance posture.
